data.description: Welcome home to this charming one-story craftsman. Come make this your home with your own finishing touches. Relax indoors and out with generous back deck overlooking the spacious fenced .38 acres. Home has newer roof and beach rights to Tiger Lake, for year round fun, motorized lake where you can fish, water ski, swim & more. Super close to Bremerton/Seabeck and 6 miles from down town Belfair. Easy commute to PSNS and all that Belfair has to offer including Belfair State Park with Hood Canal access, Gold Mountain Golf Club, Rodeo Drive-In Theater, & limitless outdoor recreational opportunities.
